 choosing a brand of business\nshirt ls exerted by husbands,\u201d\nand wives \u201care largely uncon\ncerned with the brand of shirt\ntheir husbands wear.\u201d\nAnd the same goes for cars.\n\u201cWhile a woman may decide\nshe wants s green car to match\nher hair, it\u2019s her husband who\nlooks under the hood and de- i\ncldes what make of car it will\nbe.\"\nGroundwork Laid\nAnd the same goes for liquor\nand Insurance and tires.\nBy no coincidence at all,\n\u201cTrue.\u201d the largest magazine\nin the men\u2019s field, has decided\n\u201cEnough of this \u2019woman makes 1\nthe- buying decisions\u2019 propa\nganda.\u201d and it\u2019s about to t\nlaunch a $250,000 campaign of\nits own to convince business\nmen that the American man\ndoes play a role In buying.\nIt has laid the groundwork J\nCAPITAL SECURITIES\nPHILADELPHIA-BALTIMORE STOCK EXCHANGE\nTransactions for tho ra,\nWaahlnftoi? Oh LI in li IBSO \u00b0O3\" lol* m*\u00ab uffis ffio\nlift i\u00bb* p us p\nmmwa\u00df i ikkr Jr Jr\"\nj C J.JO 46 40 44Vi 44 y\u00ab 4ft 47\nEl\u00ab\u00aba Natl Jk nmr.lL It .Vino* 140 140 lli lW li? lit\nHKfib i f *ii i is\niflpLf It jj* \\\\l 1? I R\n|&M\u201c. S* Ik\nlea Ona* BS.\n19M 129* UnItMAM 1 00 13M 129* 129*- M\n1M 1M UtdPkC Mia* 7C 1M 1M 1M- M\n49M 37 UtdShM *4*a 3C >3O SOM SOM- M\n744* 47M U S Borax N Ml 93M C7M 47M-3M\nSOM 3*M USAForS.SSg a 24 34 32M 32M- M\n34M *39* USrniChlMa 3* MM *OM *7 -*M\nC9M 51M USGypaum 2a 130 C4M CIM C* -1\n17M CM \u00dcBBofni.top ISO 0 7M 0 M\n174* 134* U tadua 1 09 139* ISM ISM- M\n374* *9M U* Liao* 7 67 ICM MM *s4*- 4*\n*79* 2>M USPipaAFI 20 93 22M *IM *IM- M\n3CM ICM U Plywd 2 74 31M 30 309*+ H\nCOM 304* U S Rubbers) ISO c*M 40 40 -6*\n**4* 174* U She* la 14 XIM *\u00a9M *l4++ M\n\u2022CM SOM U S Smelt' id 17 40 30 SO -1\n\u2022146 93 USBmit Pf34*x 754 M 53 53 -9*\n7346 9746 lit Steal 244 s 700 C4M CIM CIM-3M\n15*46 13CM US Steel pf 7 17 144 M 143 M 14346+ M\nIBM 17 \u00dcBTobl.lt 30 17M 17M 17M\nCM UtdStr*pf .3Sg 20 CM CM CM- M\nCM CM